title: New✨NoFee 1Bed/1Ba✨off L train✨Gym,Roof Terrace,Parking✨
posting_body: ['A Brand New Elevator Building in Bushwick/Ridgewood featuring Parking, Rooftop, Private Outdoor Spaces, Laundry Room, Storage, and more!', 'Multiple layouts available, I have access to all and can show a variety!', 'Units with large, private balconies also available!', 'Apartment Features:', '-Beautiful kitchen featuring all new SS appliances; 5 burner electrical stove, dishwasher, built in microwave', '-Closets in room plus hall closet', '-Nicely tiled, spacious bathroom, deep tub, built in shower shelving and floating shelves for max storage', '-Thoughtful recessed lighting', '-Video intercom', '-Central A/C', '-Hardwood floors throughout', '-Hot water included', '-Pet Friendly', '-Guarantors welcome', 'Building Amenities:', '-Laundry room', '-Garage', '-Gym Room', '-Individual storage units', '-Shared Rooftop', '*Price is Net!', '👉🏼Taking offers👈🏼', '🚇Right off the L Train via Halsey Ave', '💃Tons of restaurants, bars, shops around; Evil Twin Brewing, Queens Brewery, The Deep End, Bushwick Taco Company, Nowadays, Diner by the Izakaya, and so much more!', 'Reach out to Diana to schedule a tour!', '(347)-323-6584']
